abstract: Fifteen people believed to be illegal immigrants are missing after small boat overturns off Chinese territory of Macau.
lead_paragraph: The Chinese news media reported that 15 people were missing, and the Macau authorities said rescuers were searching for survivors.

headline.main: Migrants Said to Be Missing After Small Boat Overturns Near Macau
